            "title": "滬指開市升19點 深成指升101點再收復萬四關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段跟隨外圍向好，上證綜指以3985點開市，升19點或0.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14098點，亦升101點或0.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升28點或0.63%，開報4594點；創業板指數開市報3355點，升31點或0.96%。</p>\n</div>",
