            "title": "港股開市︱初段回升 恒指升139點報25891點 迅銷績後復牌高開3.66%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">隔晚美股持續反彈，重新帶動亞洲股市今早氣氛，港股同樣反彈。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報25891點，升139點或0.54%。恒生科技指數開報4844點，升22點或0.47；國企指數以8655點開市，升43點或0.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍造好，滙控(00005)開報139.6元，升0.5%；友邦(01299)開報90元，升1.7%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報125.1元，升1.79%；騰訊(00700)開報508元，跌0.1%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">迅銷(06288)昨天派半年成績表，盈利升19.6%，派息亦勝預期，公司隨即上調全年收益、盈利及派息預測；該股今早復牌應聲高開3.66%，以34元開市，創1個月新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：迅銷官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-web_06288-6-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：迅銷官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-web_06288-6-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：迅銷官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">尚有多家內地企業發表今年首季業績快報，相關股份不少亦在今早揚升。思摩爾(06969)開報10.08元，升2.34%；中信証券(06030)開報25.62元，升3.14%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855199-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87139%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125891%e9%bb%9e-%e8%bf%85%e9%8a%b7%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c",
